          "email": "tony@att.com",
          "username": "TonyLHansen"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2021-08-24 17:25:44.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 6: Code-Review-1\n\n(5 comments)\n\nThank you -- it's getting better.\n\nGeneric comment on ipv4 addresses:\n\nA space in the middle won't parse properly in most ipv4 parsers\n\nWithout space gives the proper behavior:\n>>> socket.gethostbyaddr(\"204.120.0.15\")\nTraceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"<stdin>\", line 1, in <module>\nsocket.herror: [Errno 1] Unknown host\n\n>>> socket.gethostbyaddr(\"127.0.0.1\")\n('localhost', ['1.0.0.127.in-addr.arpa'], ['127.0.0.1'])\n\n\nWith space gives incorrect response:\n>>> socket.gethostbyaddr(\"204.120. 0.15\")\nTraceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"<stdin>\", line 1, in <module>\nsocket.gaierror: [Errno 8] nodename nor servname provided, or not known\n>>> socket.gethostbyaddr(\"127.0.0. 1\")\nTraceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"<stdin>\", line 1, in <module>\nsocket.gaierror: [Errno 8] nodename nor servname provided, or not known\n>>>",
        "patchset_number": 6
      },
